{"tid":461983,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇龔成？","createTime":"2017-11-08T06:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T05:32:21.000Z","uid":30532,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c3746d77e9b213dab94ff1472ef57cf399c591d5","tid":461983,"uid":30532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:53:50.000Z","msg":"近排睇經濟一周先知佢係邊個 咁後生又出書又上車又財務自由好似好有料咁 咁多位巴打點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係有料到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪又係好彩冇實力<br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n龔成是於公屋長大的80後青年，畢業後於銀行從事投資相關工作，雖然月薪僅萬多元，但因為理財及投資有道，只花五年時間，於28歲已累積到100萬元資產，目前淨流動資產有數百萬元。著有暢銷書《80後百萬富翁》、《80後2百萬富翁》及《財務自由行》，並出任創富課程導師。<br />\nfacebook專頁：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/80shing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F80shing&d=MFfkkn4nI%2FJmivNoLpWHqZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=2f33afa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/80shing</a><br />\n<br />\n個人網站：<a href=\"https://80shing.skx.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F80shing.skx.io%2F&d=MFfkkn4nI%2FJmivNoLpWHqZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ec3b4aeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://80shing.skx.io/</a>"},{"pid":"06fddf045f3b71608079db4182b7c2586fd07992","tid":461983,"uid":101396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"又賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091a0036c3e321a67858d172fd282a37d3afe830","tid":461983,"uid":30532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"冇人識？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9e77c222dcf3bba757ab9f50d4c181c96ca8ca","tid":461983,"uid":30532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201